						               													<description>Relick is a card game that recreates the relick manga battles in which you will have to create your deck with one of the characters from the series and fight with different weapons and objects from retro video games such as the power glove and the plumber's star!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In the game, each player chooses a character that has a number of life points, in each turn the players can: draw 1 card, attack, use 2 cards from their hand or level up. To win you have to attack your opponent with the attack dice, if you hit the result of the dice you will subtract life points from the opponent, you can also use other cards that will allow them to reach this objective faster, when a player reaches life 0, don't lose the game, but if you manage to hurt him one more time with at least 1 damage, you win the game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
